585
00:37:01,289 --> 00:37:02,289
No.

586
00:37:02,489 --> 00:37:03,960
Let's go to the diner if you're hungry.

587
00:37:05,630 --> 00:37:06,630
No.

588
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:09,300
