613
00:38:17,130 --> 00:38:19,239
Hang on. Wait.

614
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,340
So...

615
00:38:22,809 --> 00:38:24,769
what you're saying you knew...

616
00:38:25,610 --> 00:38:28,380
