646
00:43:21,269 --> 00:43:22,300
Bye.

647
00:43:26,110 --> 00:43:27,139
Lee Hong Ju.

648
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:32,010
The fried chicken.

649
00:43:32,679 --> 00:43:33,880
Let's have it together.

650
